lyrics:
[Verse]
Haunted whispers in the night
Silent specters bathed in moonlight
Phantoms dance in ethereal glow
Lost souls yearning to let go

[Chorus]
Gho-sts, in the neon haze we glide
Gho-sts, shadows caught in time's tide
Gho-sts, drifting through the synthwave
Forever bound, yet longing to stray
